name: Yogyakarta Night Horizon (1/3)
description:
This is my story about my city, the capital city of the Special Region of Yogyakarta in Indonesia. A special city that still maintains traditional concepts and Javanese culture that has become a the residence of the Ngayogyakarta Hadiningrat Sultanate.

=====================

The center of the object in this Aerial photographic is the monument, becomes the symbol or icon of the typical city of Yogyakarta which is often known as the "Tugu Pal Putih", The monument is in the shape of an ellipse with a small ball and a pointed tip at the top. Has a magical symbolic value that connects: Parangtritis Beach, Panggung Krapyak, Ngayogyakarta Hadiningrat Palace, and Mount Merapi. Form a straight line to the top of Mount Merapi known as the Yogyakarta Imaginary Line.
.
Dimensions : (4056 x 3040)
